# Content Creation Workflow Output Directory

This directory contains in-progress content creation workflows.

## Structure

Each workflow is stored in its own subdirectory:
```
content-create/
├── 2026-01-31-ai-strategy-gap/
│   ├── 01-research.md
│   ├── 02-big-ideas.md
│   ├── ...
│   └── metadata.json
└── [another-workflow-id]/
    └── ...
```

## Cleanup

Completed workflows should be archived to History.
Delete abandoned workflows after 30 days.
